Shaun VanWeelden.description: Shaun VanWeelden is a 5th year senior studying software engineering. He's passionate about both frontend and backend development and has worked extensively with Javascript, HTML/CSS, jQuery, C#, Parse, Firebase, Java and many other web technologies. He's done web development work at Mircorosft, Amazon, and Boeing and is excited to see where his studies will take him.
